title: Oxford Talking Chinese Dictionary and Instant Translator v. 1.0.
description: Oxford&#039;s Chinese-English/English-Chinese Dictionary for Windows. Contains all Chinese characters, both traditional and simplified as well as many compounds, words, sayings and examples. Also contains pronounciation for each syllable. Great tool for quick reference. Allows you to search for whole words and part of words from both English and Chinese (characters and/or Pinyin ).
